{"tid":55706,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"搶iPhone客！ Google Drive新增備份助轉Android","createTime":"2016-12-26T15:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T10:51:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18a35c19da366608bf1b6ecc5a1af89069e053cd","tid":55706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"Google Drive最近推出了新功能，讓iOS用家也可以備份資料，方便轉會到Android。記者實試傳送iPhone 6s Plus的資料到Android機上，看看新功能的威力。<br />\n<br />\n首先登入雲端的電郵，然後按下設定備份，備份內容包括通訊錄、日曆、相片以及影片。完成備份後可以在Google相片查看備份圖片，在Android機登入相同電郵便可自行下載圖片，聯絡人、日曆等資料也可以設定為同步。記者實試後發現一些WhatsApp或遊戲程式資料無法備份，而且免費的雲端只有15GB，相片或影片超出上限也不能夠備份，除非付款增加雲端容量。<br />\n應用程式《Copy my data》支援iOS 6.0以及Android 2.3.3 或以上版本，也可以做到過資料效果，而且因為並非經過雲端，沒有15GB限制，需要連接同一個無線網絡(WiFi)才能使用。連接兩機後可以選擇互換資料，可以一次過傳送日曆、相片、影片以及聯絡人等重要資料。程式簡單易用，非常合適平常沒有習慣備份的人。<br />\n雖然新推出的雲端備份方便iOS的用家，但其功能略嫌不足，特別是備份WhatsApp資料等日常使用的工具，有待改善。<br />\n記者：翁怡富 <br />\n攝影：伍慶泉、黃子偉 <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20161226/56084529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20161226%2F56084529&d=4YjHC32Alak4kEUk3d%2FSJQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=f7a0a978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20161226%2F56084529&h=ab3bcabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20161226/56084529</a>"},{"pid":"777f2b363840663246eb7f15ccf5e77c9fc1e1c8","tid":55706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c626cb22f5467580aaed9010bcbbad559498451f","tid":55706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c3c70f81fa1efda4170627eac1a636eceda685","tid":55706,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,